00:51:25,959 --> 00:51:29,827
I'm not trying to alter anything,
just illuminate it.

718
00:51:31,364 --> 00:51:32,592
Yeah.

719
00:51:32,766 --> 00:51:36,133
You saying MacMurphy and his bunch,
yelling for my impeachment...

720
00:51:36,303 --> 00:51:39,101
...they're responsible,
law-abiding men?

721
00:51:39,372 --> 00:51:42,637
Yeah, they're responsible all right,
to Alta Power and oil companies...

722
00:51:42,809 --> 00:51:44,276
