1499
01:50:59,904 --> 01:51:01,838
...about me.

1500
01:51:02,340 --> 01:51:04,240
About you?

1501
01:51:05,844 --> 01:51:07,971
About you and the governor.
You can say it, Anne.

1502
01:51:08,146 --> 01:51:10,740
It doesn't hurt any more to hear it
than to know it.

1503
01:51:11,549 --> 01:51:13,039
He told him what I'd done...

1504
01:51:13,218 --> 01:51:15,880
...and he said that I'd do anything
to help the governor...

1505
01:51:16,054 --> 01:51:17,988
...get what he wanted.
Even if that meant...

1506
01:51:18,156 --> 01:51:20,852
...sacrificing my brother
to some kind of fraud.

1507
01:51:22,627 --> 01:51:24,857
Which is all the hospital was.

1508
01:51:25,030 --> 01:51:27,931
Nothing but a scheme to rob the state.

1509
01:51:28,099 --> 01:51:29,930
