1537
01:54:00,785 --> 01:54:03,151
<i>Bless the senators you sit among.</i>

1538
01:54:03,321 --> 01:54:06,222
<i>We place our trust
in your guidance.</i>

1539
01:54:06,391 --> 01:54:07,858
<i>You are our Lord and Savior.</i>

1540
01:54:08,393 --> 01:54:10,361
<i>- Amen.
